{"tid":1755793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支那寶account被hack 仲要瘋狂買嘢","createTime":"2019-11-25T18:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T19:23:05.000Z","uid":305257,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8620c3b5000458988e8fbf8b6fe634def0a71b","tid":1755793,"uid":305257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 本人某日突然收到一個奇怪email。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPj81a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPj81a6.png&h=0e52296e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話我咩成功退款。<br />\n<br />\n但問題係, 我已經成年幾冇用過支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: small;\">更加唔會買埋啲咩大媽衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> 我即刻check番銀行啲錢係齊嘅, 用嘅唔係我嘅錢, 我就冇點理。<br />\n<br />\n今日我心血來潮想上去睇一睇, 發現條友已經坐正咁攞我account嚟用, 買勁多大媽衫, 仲有幾件運緊過去。 #pointing#<br />\n<br />\n要點先攞得番我account嘅主導權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0251e684c3c0babb8b18c2f83e434d85509661b","tid":1755793,"uid":31173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"樓豬放上連登問會expect有咩答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875fb1850d006f39a75e6080eb486b91dcabe887","tid":1755793,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a0251e684c3c0babb8b18c2f83e434d85509661b","tid":1755793,"uid":31173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"樓豬放上連登問會expect有咩答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa